Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:03.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Takase!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:11.78,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I can't help but follow Sugawara-kun\Nwith my eyes these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:13.96,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:16.51,sign_1752_4_Tuning,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,852)}Tuning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:16.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:19.24,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You've been weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:20.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:23.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:25.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in love or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:29.53,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really, Chii-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? No, Yo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:33.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about love and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you want to\Nwhen you see everyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.79,0:01:38.32,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Goda-kun and Ayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.11,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.12,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:46.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we were {\i1}just{\i0} talking\Nabout you, Ayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.49,0:01:48.25,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Really? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ayaka-chan, how did you start\Ngoing out with Goda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know, too, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something, Ayaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:00.30,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah, I was just looking for Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we talk just a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, we shouldn't pry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.06,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, aren't you curious, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:12.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so who confessed first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:16.30,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:18.95,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:21.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.92,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}are{\i0} interested, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:23.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:26.27,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is there someone you like, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,She's been sighing nonstop lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I have not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.04,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was like that, too, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.55,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens when you like someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:38.92,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't really anyone I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:43.00,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I would follow Goda-kun\Nwith my eyes unconsciously,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.48,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,or think about him without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:47.77,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty out of it during club work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.48,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chii-chan,\Nis there seriously no one you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:57.95,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun's just a classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:02.00,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's kind to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.28,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Sugawara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:05.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:06.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why would you guess Sugawara-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:11.87,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, it's just a rumor that I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.22,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,That he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:18.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that rumor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.34,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun likes me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.01,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun does?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.07,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sugawara-kun does?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.00,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Suga—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.18,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a rumor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe if you confessed to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not going to, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:39.03,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how did you confess, Ayaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.53,Default,Girl 2,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:46.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.98,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.30,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.02,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we get back together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Like, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:03.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kana, about the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.57,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But, Chiaki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.12,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:06.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.69,sign_6037_75_Water_Under_the_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,500)}Water Under the Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.56,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:18.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why'd you break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.94,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Because he gave the weirdest first kiss ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I do agree he messed up,\Nbut are you sure you really want to break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.79,sign_6469_81_I_m_really_sorry,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry! \N\NAre you still angry? \N\NSee you at school tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.82,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Still no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.44,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Not even marked as read.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.34,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll stop messaging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.68,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I've been ignoring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.79,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Should I forgive him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.76,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like Chiaki was {\i0}trying{\i1} to be awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.06,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.60,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't reply\Nafter one more message, I'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.60,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If he apologizes one more time,\NI'll forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.60,sign_7053_91_I_m_really_sorry,Text,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about what happened.\N I won't try to pull weird kisses anymore. \NCan you forgive me?\N I miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:59.12,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a long letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.66,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be too creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.20,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's been messaging me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.19,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why not today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.45,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and apologize, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.45,sign_7420_97_Can_I_call_you_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Can I call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.10,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the best way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.96,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize directly if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:29.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:31.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.82,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What did he want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.10,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.84,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't leave her phone\Neven when she takes a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:49.91,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally ignoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.40,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.22,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he was apologizing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.75,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to reply tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.89,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.46,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But what if Chiaki gives up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.70,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,After how long I've ignored him,\Nhe might just quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.22,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He might even hate me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:08.57,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:12.22,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He pisses me off sometimes, but I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.90,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I want to apologize to {\i0}him{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.39,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.46,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.31,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.68,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Turn on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.94,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kana, are you ever coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.56,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing undressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my phone in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Just give it a good whack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What if it gets even worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:41.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good with technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.13,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:48.94,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.51,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let me apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.43,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:53.93,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the phone, Kana!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:55.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:56.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:01.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She hung up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:03.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:06.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'm blocking you, too, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.89,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What? It broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem with technology!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.03,sign_10359_140_Class_2_1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:17.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I forget my pencil leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:19.75,sign_10433_143_Exam,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,500)}Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.04,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:26.30,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If I gave her my pencil leads,\Nwould she think I had ulterior motives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.37,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If I asked Takase instead of my girl friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.37,0:07:32.37,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,for a pencil lead, would he think\NI had ulterior motives?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:39.68,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean, I {\i0}do{\i1} have an ulterior motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.31,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right, take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:43.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan, can I have some pencil leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:47.16,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my pencil leads are 0.4 millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:50.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask Takase-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.02,0:07:51.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You sit next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's your chance to get close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't bring that up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:01.46,sign_11484_157_Final_Exams,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Final Exams
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.96,sign_11544_158_Second_year_Engl,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Second-year English Exam Answer Sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.85,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I'm already out of lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.46,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I should have asked Takase.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:16.85,sign_10359_140_Class_2_1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Class 2-1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:14.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.61,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pass your answer sheets towards the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:22.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you mine sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:29.93,Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't they going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.69,sign_12233_169_Solving_for_x_in,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Solving for x in ax=b \N1. When a ≠ 0: \Nx = b/a \N2. When a = 0: \NWhen b = 0: x is any real number \N(Because it's of the form 0x = 0) \NWhen b ≠ 0: No solutions\N (Because it's of the form 0x ≠ 0)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.69,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:36.00,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,The solution of ax = b is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.52,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,x equals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.74,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is this wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.38,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:42.92,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're already in third year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:45.46,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it too late to start studying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:47.97,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's why I'm studying now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.96,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have money, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.00,Flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,Going to college is one thing, but private?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.35,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.46,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.48,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said to my mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:59.97,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,but am I really going to make it\Ninto public college, studying now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.20,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:09.44,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I skipped or slept through\Nall my exams until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.36,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:17.86,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,everyone else looks better than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.37,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I think I really did start too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.68,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.88,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:36.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Was Kaji always so studious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.95,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.32,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,She's awoken to the fact\Nthat exams are approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:42.71,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,You could learn from her, Kyouko-san—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.88,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's her man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:47.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, isn't she dating\Nthe student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:57.36,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,Masafumi, your girl looks tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.00,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of her practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be alone at the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:09.60,Default,God,0000,0000,0000,,You say that, but {\i1}you're{\i0} the one\Nwho's trying not to freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:13.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me if I try to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.17,Italics,God,0000,0000,0000,,Snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm handing out exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Take your seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.39,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.49,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what you learned with Akagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.18,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko-chan, that question there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.30,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.32,Flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Can I kiss you when you're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.46,Flashback,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:28.56,sign_15051_214_Fundamentals_of_,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Fundamentals of Exam Problems\N {\fs25}Mathematics III
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.56,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:37.07,Italics,God,0000,0000,0000,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.04,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.21,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i0}think{\i1} I answered it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:45.22,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did I seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.84,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.61,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I reviewed it over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.58,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get this right\Nand go to college with Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:57.97,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.43,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you do in these situations again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:03.01,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, tell the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.60,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't people think
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:13.52,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weird if I raise my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.04,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,"There's a delinquent taking the exams."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.82,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,"She's trying to go to college."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.19,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.46,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how hard I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:26.41,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, could you please pick up this eraser?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:28.84,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.05,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.82,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:33.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Kaji-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.42,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.42,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're working hard this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.48,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Break a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.18,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:00.75,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.31,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Are you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:03.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.65,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Was it something I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.65,0:12:06.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.13,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:09.31,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:12.92,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,I want to nap in the nurse's office, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.52,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now, Sano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.25,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Get back to the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Summer Is Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:29.89,sign_17932_255_Summer_Is_Coming,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,1)}Summer Is Coming
